OpenVPN easy-rsa 2.2.2 docker wrapper.

# Build instructions #
Build the docker with the following command:
docker build -t new-easy-rsa .

# Run instructions #
Run *.sh scripts to perform desired operations:
- gen_ca.sh generates a CA key-pair and certificate, and computes a new DH file.
- gen_client.sh generates a client key-pair and certificate, signed by CA.
- gen_server.sh generates a server key-pair and certificate, signed by CA.

# Custom configuration #
Use vars file to customize easy-rsa. See easy-rsa documentation here
https://github.com/OpenVPN/easy-rsa/blob/release/2.x/easy-rsa/2.0/vars
